text: The Evangelical Free Church in Sweden (), "EFK", is a Christian Protestant denomination in Sweden. It was established in 1997 as a merger out of Örebro Mission (Örebromissionen, founded in 1892 as Örebro Missionary Society), the Free Baptist Union (Fribaptistsamfundet, founded in 1872) and the Sanctification Union (Helgelseförbundet, founded in 1887). ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1997 establishments in Sweden Category:Baptist churches Category:Protestantism in Sweden
title: Evangelical Free Church in Sweden
